Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.56,0:00:48.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.20,0:00:57.76,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? So you're off to Mistral?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.76,0:00:59.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hard stuff there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.12,0:01:03.68,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But the food is good, and they say the women are lookers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.68,0:01:06.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,About half a year since the truce?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.66,0:01:10.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And with that. Happy I'm still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.81,0:01:12.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,See? Grim Bourlouge.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.91,0:01:16.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh please.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.56,0:01:15.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't beat that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.87,0:01:16.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.30,0:01:17.54,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dammit again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.96,0:01:20.54,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey miss. Awake there?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.82,0:01:24.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Your share of the booty.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.36,0:01:27.89,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Caramel?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.60,0:01:32.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a fancy thing. It's too kind of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.02,0:01:35.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sergeant!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.19,0:01:38.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mention it. Being nice to the bugler means
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.32,0:01:40.81,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,you hear the retreat calls clearer, so they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.29,0:01:43.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,With the draft gone and all,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.31,0:01:45.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,it's rare to see new recruits.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.41,0:01:46.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You volunteer for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.75,0:01:47.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.80,0:01:49.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to learn the trumpet-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.45,0:01:50.42,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.35,0:01:52.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.21,0:01:55.84,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Good! An honest one!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.84,0:01:57.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck there, miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.66,0:01:59.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name, private?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.69,0:02:00.65,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:03.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata Sorami.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.39,0:02:12.44,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,3600)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord0}so ra no wo to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.24,0:02:26.58,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}The brilliant glow of this sky, does it carry right into your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.20,0:02:36.55,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,1600)}The melody you heard in your dream, it plays like the silence
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.84,0:02:41.84,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}Even if your hands are still far from that dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.88,0:02:46.85,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}Come now and remember that kindly voice
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.85,0:02:59.61,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(50,200)}Someone was there singing for you, the happiness they sang about
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.61,0:03:09.08,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}Sound of the sky, echo on high, break through that overwhelming sadness
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.16,0:03:13.92,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}Everything that shines in your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.00,0:03:19.59,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,400)}Is part of the real world
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.67,0:03:28.81,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,200)}Even your tears can't leave you here to stay forever
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.97,0:03:41.24,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,4000)}In this light pouring down onto you, play tomorrow's song
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.41,0:03:55.42,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\bord0}Echoing Sound - Town at Daybreak
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:16.47,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a festival in Seize today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.47,0:04:17.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.06,0:04:19.65,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm leaving you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.43,0:04:27.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.66,0:04:31.33,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's your assignment. They call it the "Time-Telling Fortress".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.33,0:04:33.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Set a course and walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.48,0:04:34.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.07,0:04:38.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Appointment:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.94,0:04:40.67,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Private Kanata Sorami.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.02,0:04:42.46,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Seize, Trois region.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.67,0:04:45.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You are assigned to Platoon 1121.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.81,0:04:49.22,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,General Headquarters of the Armed Forces of the Republic of Helvetia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:01.67,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,1320.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.84,0:05:02.89,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mission complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.89,0:05:04.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.47,0:05:17.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The town of lakes and glass,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.90,0:05:18.90,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Seize.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.18,0:05:23.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.57,0:05:26.51,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Assignment time is 1500.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.92,0:05:30.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally get to let you sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.42,0:05:36.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Bearing: confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.52,0:05:38.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Assignment time: confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.60,0:05:40.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Equipment: confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.47,0:05:43.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Forward march!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.88,0:06:22.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,G-flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.78,0:06:24.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A beautiful sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.28,0:06:28.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.52,0:06:31.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,￥ 10.25.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.13,0:06:40.54,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pretty doll-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.95,0:06:43.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.61,0:06:47.17,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.17,0:06:49.17,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A kitten, drunk in the merriment
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.91,0:06:52.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,was running full-speed into places it shouldn't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.82,0:06:54.47,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you can't help that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:57.47,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kittens thrive on what they find in the streets.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.09,0:07:00.54,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that why they're cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.77,0:07:05.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe for stray cats.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.34,0:07:09.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, it was a pet cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.64,0:07:30.51,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That was scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.33,0:07:35.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But I found another wonderful thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.21,0:07:41.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.35,0:07:45.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.87,0:07:58.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.09,0:07:59.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,One of the girls in the fortress?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.31,0:08:01.08,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Now here's something to celebrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:02.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,For the fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.36,0:08:03.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.84,0:08:25.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.70,0:08:27.86,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.27,0:08:29.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.27,0:08:30.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.41,0:08:32.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:34.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.14,0:08:57.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.72,0:09:02.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you an idiot? Getting completely caught up in the festivities.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.50,0:09:04.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going looking like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.34,0:09:13.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Gesundheit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.91,0:09:14.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank y-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.85,0:09:22.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.72,0:09:36.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How's the water?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.79,0:09:39.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.45,0:09:40.76,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.01,0:09:44.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It does look like you did quite a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.43,0:09:46.47,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't at least dodge it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.93,0:09:51.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This dye goes away when it dries.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.27,0:09:53.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.35,0:09:57.22,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the festival, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.22,0:09:59.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a legend here in Seize.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.01,0:10:02.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A legend? What kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.19,0:10:05.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The Maidens of Fire
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.80,0:10:08.22,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,protect the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.52,0:10:21.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for all the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.35,0:10:24.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll add it on. I finished repairing that thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.95,0:10:28.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.14,0:10:30.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.62,0:10:34.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Felicia?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.83,0:10:38.17,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That meddling...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.70,0:10:39.84,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.51,0:10:43.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Late, late, late!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.99,0:10:46.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We even came all the way out here for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.35,0:10:47.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.62,0:10:49.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's stand at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.61,0:10:53.81,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a present from your father, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.44,0:10:55.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.49,0:10:58.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,D-flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.77,0:11:03.08,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for letting me use your bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.80,0:11:07.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I tend to get lost on the road...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.78,0:11:10.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm thankful that I was able to meet such a wonderful person!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.75,0:11:15.08,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome. But don't get lost up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.99,0:11:30.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You... know the sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.25,0:11:41.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a clear... somewhat familiar sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.46,0:11:44.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mean like th-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.79,0:11:47.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.04,0:11:48.14,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.91,0:11:56.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.82,0:11:57.98,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.48,0:12:00.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you going to die for that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.08,0:12:02.47,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But that bell...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.88,0:12:06.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.65,0:12:08.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.17,0:12:10.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,this is how it should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.08,0:12:17.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.68,0:12:22.76,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.09,0:12:28.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\an3}Sound of the Skies
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.98,0:12:39.98,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\an1}Sound of the Skies
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.91,0:12:41.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.85,0:12:44.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I have some business to attend to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.07,0:12:45.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get lost again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.51,0:12:48.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That bell...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.51,0:12:51.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be important to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.83,0:12:53.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.42,0:12:59.67,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.53,0:13:06.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.81,0:13:18.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Forward march!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.50,0:14:13.25,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,The Maidens of Fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.88,0:14:17.29,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,A long time ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.02,0:14:22.46,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,long before the world turned out this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.11,0:14:29.73,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,a winged demon lived at the bottom of this town's valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.28,0:14:34.36,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,The demon
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:36.25,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,spat fire,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.86,0:14:38.40,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,shook the earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.14,0:14:41.27,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,and caused the people suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.58,0:14:48.17,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, it carried off the maidens that lived in the fortress,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.40,0:14:51.69,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,and held them in an underground labyrinth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.33,0:14:59.59,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,But
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.43,0:15:02.38,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,The Maidens lost no heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.72,0:15:04.59,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,Calling to each other with golden horns,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.13,0:15:07.08,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,granted to them by an angel,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.13,0:15:10.21,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,they escaped the labyrinth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.28,0:15:13.62,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,With the aid of a giant spider,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.40,0:15:17.95,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,they defeated the demon and took its head.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.28,0:15:23.39,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,When they did, an intense fire sprung from the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.98,0:15:28.22,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,If left alone, the town above would burn to the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.63,0:15:32.28,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,To keep the springing fire from the town, the Maidens,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.57,0:15:33.95,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,each in turn,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.95,0:15:36.54,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,held the head of the demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.15,0:15:40.37,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,Every day, the townspeople cast water upon the flaming head
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.38,0:15:43.62,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,and upon the Maidens.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.88,0:15:47.27,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,After one year, the fire had gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.07,0:15:52.13,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,Since then, to console the spirits of the Maidens who saved the town,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:55.78,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,they have celebrated the Water-Casting Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.54,0:16:52.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.19,0:16:53.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The new recruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.49,0:16:55.59,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.59,0:16:58.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Commander! It's Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.09,0:17:01.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It does look good on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.36,0:17:05.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I was right leaving it to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.01,0:17:06.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But we drew straws to de-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.62,0:17:16.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I got lost again...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.61,0:17:21.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just hopeless...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.57,0:17:33.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There are times when it's fun to get lost,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.92,0:17:39.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,but that's because you might meet someone new.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.83,0:17:43.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Being all alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.33,0:17:45.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,isn't fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.88,0:17:48.08,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,Lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.42,0:17:51.20,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.40,0:17:52.34,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.86,0:17:55.85,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wish for it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.74,0:17:58.85,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,your wish will reach her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.15,0:18:00.31,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.31,0:18:01.02,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.32,0:18:03.27,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,The sound will surely echo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.65,0:18:06.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely echo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.33,0:18:09.18,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely echo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.61,0:18:13.23,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,100)}and reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.97,0:18:16.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Maidens of Fire,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.66,0:18:17.98,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,rest in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.73,0:18:21.88,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold the demon, and silence its curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.48,0:18:26.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,May you never need to wake again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.35,0:18:27.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.48,0:18:29.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A golden horn?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.93,0:18:31.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The demon can't have...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.48,0:18:32.90,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Have they awakened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.40,0:18:34.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.01,0:18:45.09,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,Reach!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.42,0:18:49.35,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone! Hear my sound!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.32,0:19:01.59,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It reached.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.30,0:19:08.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The sound will echo,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.94,0:19:10.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,and...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.63,0:19:15.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and wake up,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.59,0:19:17.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Private Kanata Sorami!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.31,0:19:24.22,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.11,0:19:26.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.12,0:19:27.66,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How long does your brain plan on sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.68,0:19:29.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Time-Telling Fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.55,0:19:32.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The garrison for Platoon 1121.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.07,0:19:49.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.99,0:19:51.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.39,0:19:53.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for causing you so much trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.20,0:19:55.54,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.54,0:19:57.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.35,0:19:59.05,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.25,0:20:00.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.48,0:20:03.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But no more of this nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.78,0:20:06.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,For a bell like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.32,0:20:29.46,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.59,0:20:31.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A trumpet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.09,0:20:35.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why this fortress is called the Time-Telling Fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.90,0:21:13.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the sound of the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.62,0:21:50.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio Kazumiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.68,0:21:52.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.69,0:21:57.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be your bugling mentor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.86,0:22:01.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I place myself in your hands, Master Sergeant Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.11,0:22:03.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.95,0:22:04.89,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Felicia-
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.90,0:22:08.63,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Our Commander's policy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.15,0:22:10.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no ranks here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.08,0:22:14.98,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.76,0:22:19.46,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's start now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.02,0:22:21.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The Reveille! Try playing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.54,0:22:41.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's girl isn't very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.66,0:22:58.22,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Love and friendship - put these feelings together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.58,0:23:01.69,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}And sing of how important they are
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.87,0:23:19.45,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I was so happy that I cried
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.63,0:23:25.54,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}It hurt so bad that I laughed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.63,0:23:34.32,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}But that all just goes to show that I'm alive
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.55,0:23:38.92,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,800)}Let's just take it easy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.95,0:23:40.55,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&}Everybody singing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.64,0:23:44.89,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Can you tell me who you're asking to the dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.97,0:23:46.10,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&}You're just my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.10,0:23:51.94,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Love and friendship - even though they might waver
Dialogue: 1,0:23:49.53,0:23:51.94,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\an8\3c&HE5A9EA&}I know, you know, we'll be happy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.12,0:23:57.91,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I want us to echo on forever
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.12,0:23:57.91,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\an8\3c&HE5A9EA&}Can you count my precious hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.28,0:24:03.91,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}All the usual words can't even describe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.17,0:24:09.75,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1000)}Our harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.07,0:24:14.70,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1000)}Can you hear it? Our harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.62,0:24:26.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(320,180)\c&H020202&\bord0}Next time: First Battle - Talk of a Chair
